Create a pokédex web app using the publicly available http://pokeapi.co/. Since we’re all about the classics, please limit the pokédex to the original 151 pokémon. 
 
Minimum requirements:

be able to search pokémon by either of the following:

- name or id
- type
- display search results with
- name and id
- height and weight
- types

species habitat(s) and English flavor text

thumbnail (the api does include some small sprites; for larger images another possible source is https://img.pokemondb.net/artw ork/bulbasaur.jpg)

Note: you only need to worry about exact matches, not partials.